answer:
a) \[ \frac{6ab^{2}}{9a^{3}b}=\frac{3ab.2b}{3ab.3a^{2}}=\frac{2b}{3a^{2}} \];
b) \[ \frac{2y-2x}{\left(x-y\right)^{2}}=\frac{-2\left(x-y\right)}{\left(x-y\right)^{2}}=\frac{-2}{x-y}=\frac{2}{y-x} \];
c) \[ \frac{a^{2}+ab}{2b^{2}+2ab}=\frac{a\left(a+b\right)}{2b\left(b+a\right)}=\frac{a}{2b}=\frac{a.2b}{2b.2b}=\frac{2ab}{4b^{2}} \].

