a) y = 3sin x + 5;
b) $y=\sqrt{1+cos2x}+3$ ;
c) y = 4 – 2sin x cos x;
d) \[ y=\frac{1}{4−sinx} \] .

answer:
Đáp án đúng là: D
Ta có \[ u_{2}=\frac{1}{3}\left(u_{2−1}+1\right)=\frac{1}{3}\left(u_{1}+1\right)=\frac{1}{3}\left(2+1\right)=1 \] ;
\[ u_{3}=\frac{1}{3}\left(u_{3−1}+1\right)=\frac{1}{3}\left(u_{3}+1\right)=\frac{1}{3}\left(1+1\right)=\frac{2}{3} \];
